{"tid":1949243,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"31歲男警初步確診　過去14日曾參與反罪惡巡邏","createTime":"2020-03-29T13:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T13:36:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad68f76fec70399568adfee6006ba00ec7e8eb8","tid":1949243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"【21:28】警方今晚（29日）於facebook發文表示，一名駐守西九龍總區的31歲男警員初步確診新型冠狀病毒。該名警員隸屬機動部隊，過去14日曾參與反罪惡巡邏，沒有外遊紀錄。他今日感到不適，到公立醫院求醫，初步測試對新冠病毒呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n【18:12】消息稱，一名駐守西九龍總區的軍裝男警初步確診，正留醫明愛醫院；他沒與較早前確診、隸屬深水埗警署的女警接觸。"},{"pid":"216227fecea03b98aafa65ea1aa732e339ee87aa","tid":1949243,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"[更新版]到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5afba0822264a9f43b3b8d2ba1ca0b88bc0cab04","tid":1949243,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}